text: On the topic of Smart Contracts vs. Legal contracts that I mentioned earlier, here is a great paper that articulates how it works, and explaining how chaincode fits next to legal text. Definitely something that should be incorporated in the design of hyperledger/fabric - <https://www.w3.org/2016/04/blockchain-workshop/interest/hazard-hardjono.html>. Topic to be discussed during the W3C workshop at the end of the month.
